               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380402-name-621" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-621" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-621" type="surname" value="FLANNAGAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-621" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>DAVID FLANNAGAN</persName>
                  </hi>. On the 12th of March, I landed from the ship <hi rend="italic">Liverpool</hi> on board which I had been steward—I had a bundle containing all these things—I went to the Queen's Head to get some refreshment, and saw the prisoner there—he drank with me, and then we went out—I had my bundle under my arm—I turned to stop for a moment, and as I did so the prisoner snatched the bundle from me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did not you invite me to a friend's house? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
